                        <ns0:remarks>The aim of the project is to re-evaluate the 400 preserved ancient sundials on the basis of new extensive 3D-measurements. 3D-measurements of the sundials form the basis for the subsequent investigation of the building processes of the sundials. It will allow insights into the diffusion of knowledge in antiquity which enabled the production of sundials.
Ancient Sundials is part of Edition Topoi Collections http://repository.edition-topoi.org/</ns0:remarks>
